{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"dgettext"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"domain","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","text":"UnsafePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gchar","text":"gchar"},{"text":">? = nil, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"msgid","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","text":"UnsafePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gchar","text":"gchar","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":">!) -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"},{"text":"!","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The advantage of using this function over ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"dgettext()"},{"type":"text","text":" proper is that"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"libraries using this function (like GTK) will not use translations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"if the application using the library does not have translations for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the current locale.  This results in a consistent English-only","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"interface instead of one having partial translations.  For this","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"feature to work, the call to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textdomain()"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setlocale()"},{"type":"text","text":" should"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"precede any "},{"code":"g_dgettext()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" invocations.  For GTK, it means calling","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"textdomain()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" before gtk_init or its variants.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This function disables translations if and only if upon its first"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"call all the following conditions hold:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"domain","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is not "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"textdomain()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" has been called to set a default text domain","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"there is no translations available for the default text domain","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and the current locale","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"current locale is not “C” or any English locales (those"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"starting with “en_”)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that this behavior may not be desired for example if an application"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"has its untranslated messages in a language other than English. In those","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"cases the application should call ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textdomain()"},{"type":"text","text":" after initializing GTK."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Applications should normally not use this function directly,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"but use the ","type":"text"},{"code":"_()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" macro for translations."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib"]]},"identifier":